<text id="02-output-contract" title="Business Process Analysis Output Contract" version="1.1.0" est_tokens="850" depth="essential">
  <summary>Pins the shape of the process-analysis report. Subagent must satisfy this before returning.</summary>
  <section title="JSON Schema (draft-07)">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/business-process-analysis-report.json",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["process_id", "current_state", "analysis", "future_state", "signoffs"],
  "properties": {
    "process_id": {"type": "string", "minLength": 2},
    "current_state": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": ["steps", "lanes"],
      "properties": {
        "steps": {
          "type": "array", "minItems": 1,
          "items": {
            "type": "object",
            "required": ["id", "lane", "description", "source"],
            "properties": {
              "id": {"type": "string"},
              "lane": {"type": "string"},
              "description": {"type": "string"},
              "source": {"type": "string", "minLength": 4}
            }
          }
        },
        "lanes": {
          "type": "array", "minItems": 1,
          "items": {
            "type": "object",
            "required": ["name", "owner_name", "owner_role"],
            "properties": {
              "name": {"type": "string"},
              "owner_name": {"type": "string", "minLength": 2},
              "owner_role": {"type": "string", "minLength": 2}
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "analysis": {
      "type": "array", "minItems": 1,
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["step_id", "value_add", "cycle_time_min", "cost_usd"],
        "properties": {
          "step_id": {"type": "string"},
          "value_add": {"type": "boolean"},
          "cycle_time_min": {"type": "number", "minimum": 0},
          "cost_usd": {"type": "number", "minimum": 0}
        }
      }
    },
    "future_state": {
      "type": "array", "minItems": 1,
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["step_id", "action", "expected_delta"],
        "properties": {
          "step_id": {"type": "string"},
          "action": {"type": "string", "enum": ["keep", "cut", "change", "add"]},
          "expected_delta": {"type": "string", "minLength": 4}
        }
      }
    },
    "signoffs": {
      "type": "array", "minItems": 1,
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["lane", "owner_name", "signoff_ts", "channel"],
        "properties": {
          "lane": {"type": "string"},
          "owner_name": {"type": "string"},
          "signoff_ts": {"type": "string", "format": "date-time"},
          "channel": {"type": "string", "enum": ["pr_comment", "email", "slack_ack"]}
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false
}
]]></code>
  </section>
  <section title="Examples">
    <example type="good" title="Valid report fragment">
      <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "process_id": "invoice-approval",
  "current_state": {
    "steps": [{"id": "s-01", "lane": "AP", "description": "Receive invoice email", "source": "ops/sop.md#L12"}],
    "lanes": [{"name": "AP", "owner_name": "Maria Lopes", "owner_role": "AP Lead"}]
  },
  "analysis": [{"step_id": "s-01", "value_add": false, "cycle_time_min": 5, "cost_usd": 1.2}],
  "future_state": [{"step_id": "s-01", "action": "change", "expected_delta": "auto-ingest via Mailgun webhook; -4 min"}],
  "signoffs": [{"lane": "AP", "owner_name": "Maria Lopes", "signoff_ts": "2026-05-23T10:00:00Z", "channel": "pr_comment"}]
}
]]></code>
      <note>All required sections present; sources cited; named owner; quantified deltas; signoff timestamp.</note>
    </example>
    <example type="bad" title="Invalid — anonymous lane">
      <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{"process_id": "x", "current_state": {"steps": [], "lanes": [{"name": "Ops", "owner_name": "Team", "owner_role": "?"}]}, "analysis": [], "future_state": [], "signoffs": []}
]]></code>
      <note>Anonymous owner ("Team") fails r2; empty arrays fail minItems.</note>
    </example>
  </section>
  <section title="Forbidden patterns">
    <list>
      <item>steps without source citation (rule r1)</item>
      <item>anonymous lane owner ("Team", "Ops") (rule r2)</item>
      <item>analysis row missing any of value_add / cycle_time_min / cost_usd (rule r3)</item>
      <item>prose future-state without diff table (rule r4)</item>
      <item>missing signoffs[] entry for any lane (rule r5)</item>
    </list>
  </section>
  <section title="Allowed transformations">
    <list>
      <item>Cycle-time can be averaged across observed instances if n &gt;= 5.</item>
      <item>Cost can be approximated from FTE rate × cycle_time when invoice data missing.</item>
    </list>
  </section>
  <reference path="templates/process-analysis.md"/>
  <reference path="scripts/validate-business-process-analysis.py"/>
</text>
